### Research Run Protocol (all multilingual-research runs)

Every run, in strict order:
1. `research-log-manager CHECK` (normalise slug; confirm STALE/PARTIAL/NOT FOUND)
2. `keyword-lookup` for target slug's concept group (native-language aliases)
3. `view` Keyword Compendium Part 3 for target slug (concept boundary warnings)
4. `view` Protocol v4 §COMPANION NETWORKS for target population code(s)
5. Build 24-jurisdiction work list
6. Execute Steps 1–5 per multilingual-research skill (Co-1 first; no exceptions)
7. Pre-LOG completeness check (7 conditions)
8. `research-log-manager LOG` (write only if all blockers clear or explicitly accepted)

